<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<title>uitox vendor</title>
<link href="../../css/plugin/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
<link href="../../css/layout.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
<link href="../../css/product.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
<style>
img {margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 3px; border: #ccc 1px solid;}
</style>
<!--[if lt IE 9]>
<script src="../../js/lib/html5.js"></script>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/ie.css">
<![endif]--></head>
<body>
<div class="popup-content">
  <h1 class="title"><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>圖檔上傳說明</h1>
  <dl class="popup-list">
    <dd>1. 圖檔整理在資料夾中，或是一個目錄下有多個資料夾</dd>
    <dd><img src="../../img/infr-img-import1.jpg" alt="圖檔整理在資料夾中"></dd>
    <dd>2. 將圖檔資料夾壓縮成zip檔案，每一個檔案不可超過20mb</dd>
    <dd><img src="../../img/infr-img-import2.jpg" alt="將圖檔資料夾壓縮成zip檔案"></dd>
    <dd>3. 選擇要匯入對應圖檔的廠商</dd>
    <dd><img src="../../img/infr-img-import3.jpg" alt="選擇廠商"></dd>
    <dd>4. 圖檔的配對規則：EXCEL填入的主商品圖名稱必須是完整的檔名。(範例：mini_ipad_black.jpg)</dd>
    <dd><img src="../../img/infr-img-import4.jpg" alt="EXCEL填入的主商品圖名稱"></dd>
  </dl>
  <div class="template-button">
    <button class="btn-cancel" onclick="parent.$.fancybox.close();"><i class="fa fa-times"></i>關閉</button>
  </div>
</div><script src="../../js/lib/jquery-1.9.1.js" ></script>
<script src="../../js/lib/bootstrap-dropdown.js"></script>
<script src="../../js/nav-action.js"></script>
</body>
</html>